<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In 2005, Ogunlesi, then a top banker at Credit=
 Suisse, was summoned to Omaha, Nebraska, by the energy arm of Warren Buffe=
tt=E2=80=99s Berkshire Hathaway to study a large takeover. It was the kind =
of call most financiers dream of, but Ogunlesi complained to his wife: =E2=
=80=9CI really don=E2=80=99t want to go.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In an interview with the Financial Times, he s=
aid his wife offered an ultimatum: =E2=80=9CEither you decide you like your=
 job and you want to keep doing it. Or, if you decide you don=E2=80=99t, go=
